Package: bridle
Title: AI Knowledge Harness Generation Framework for R Statistical Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Katsuya", "Shibuki", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "shibuki@example.com")
Description: Generates knowledge harnesses that structure R package knowledge
    and deliver it to LLMs for statistical analysis guidance. The LLM presents
    considerations and suggestions based on a curated knowledge base while the
    user makes the final decision.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/shibuki/bridle
BugReports: https://github.com/shibuki/bridle/issues
